<p>一年一度的，除了天香楼的大闸蟹外，还有8½ Otto e Mezzo的白松露。白松露菌当造于每年10月至12月，我们一家6口今天特意前来为宝贝妹妺庆祝她的正日生日。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>白松露的香甜味道令我为之疯狂，8½的白松露是来自意大利古城Alba，是最顶级的品种。白松露遇火会走味，8½的white truffle menu全部都于客人面前即刨，而且份量超多，保证香气四射。这里的白松露Menu有:lobster salad, scramble egg, poached egg, homemade pasta and Deer Loin，每份分别索价$920元，。我们都选择white truffle配温泉蛋，poached egg 味道最纯，最能够全神地保留白松露的香浓。</p><p><br/></p><p style="text-align: center"><img src="http://7xj9od.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/1458032292000111.jpg?imageView2/2/w/1000|watermark/1/image/aHR0cDovLzd4ajlvZC5jb20yLnowLmdsYi5xaW5pdWNkbi5jb20vd2F0ZXJtYXJrLnBuZw==/dissolve/50/gravity/SouthEast/dx/10/dy/10"height="175" width="240"/></p><p>Poach Egg with White Truffles HK$ 920<br/></p><p>白松露的份量真的多到盖住了温泉和碟底的炒磨菇，Manager Andy笑着同我地道歉，说白松露太多，让我们拍不到那个蛋。看，这不就是又亲切又高级的service，其他米芝莲服务员请学一下他，有笑容又helpful。</p><p><br/></p><p style="text-align: center"><img src="http://7xj9od.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/1458032313000517.jpg?imageView2/2/w/1000|watermark/1/image/aHR0cDovLzd4ajlvZC5jb20yLnowLmdsYi5xaW5pdWNkbi5jb20vd2F0ZXJtYXJrLnBuZw==/dissolve/50/gravity/SouthEast/dx/10/dy/10"height="164" width="240"/></p><p>Egg with White Truffles HK$ 920<br/></p><p><br/></p><p style="text-align: center"><img src="http://7xj9od.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/145803232500049.jpg?imageView2/2/w/1000|watermark/1/image/aHR0cDovLzd4ajlvZC5jb20yLnowLmdsYi5xaW5pdWNkbi5jb20vd2F0ZXJtYXJrLnBuZw==/dissolve/50/gravity/SouthEast/dx/10/dy/10"height="180" width="240"/></p><p>Egg with White Truffles HK$ 920<br/></p><p>White Truffle Tangliolini 是另一必食的白松露菜式，只有这道菜才是由Chef Umberto Bombana亲自刨白松露的。Chef Bombana非常亲切，笑容满面且无架子。</p><p><br/></p><p style="text-align: center"><img src="http://7xj9od.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/145803233600039.jpg?imageView2/2/w/1000|watermark/1/image/aHR0cDovLzd4ajlvZC5jb20yLnowLmdsYi5xaW5pdWNkbi5jb20vd2F0ZXJtYXJrLnBuZw==/dissolve/50/gravity/SouthEast/dx/10/dy/10"/height="285" width="240"></p><p>Chef Umberto Bombana preparing white truffles<br/></p><p>这盘白松露应该是他才可处理，Chef Bombana十分熟练地将不同的白松露刨落啲手造蛋面上。每棵白松露的气味及浓度都不一样，Chef Bombana用他对白松露的认识将他们mix and match，为我们泡制出一度非常精彩的白松露蛋面。</p><p><br/></p><p style="text-align: center"><img src="http://7xj9od.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/145803234700089.jpg?imageView2/2/w/1000|watermark/1/image/aHR0cDovLzd4ajlvZC5jb20yLnowLmdsYi5xaW5pdWNkbi5jb20vd2F0ZXJtYXJrLnBuZw==/dissolve/50/gravity/SouthEast/dx/10/dy/10"/height="163" width="240"></p><p>White Truffles<br/></p><p>这度Handmade Tangliolini同之前的温泉蛋一样，白松露多到铺满整个碟，嗅觉上比温泉蛋更香。Tangliolini只用少量牛油同parmesan cheese去调味，保持了蛋面的蛋香。面质爽滑，连白松露一起食，实在是太好吃了。这面没下太多酱汁，我喜欢这种吃法，吃到最后还是很爽口弹牙，白松露的精华及香味亦全保留在最后的那一口汤上面。。</p><p><br/></p><p style="text-align: center"><img src="http://7xj9od.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/1458032359000514.jpg?imageView2/2/w/1000|watermark/1/image/aHR0cDovLzd4ajlvZC5jb20yLnowLmdsYi5xaW5pdWNkbi5jb20vd2F0ZXJtYXJrLnBuZw==/dissolve/50/gravity/SouthEast/dx/10/dy/10"height="170" width="240"/></p><p>White Truffle Tangliolini HK$ 920<br/></p><p><br/></p><p style="text-align: center"><img src="http://7xj9od.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/145803236900072.jpg?imageView2/2/w/1000|watermark/1/image/aHR0cDovLzd4ajlvZC5jb20yLnowLmdsYi5xaW5pdWNkbi5jb20vd2F0ZXJtYXJrLnBuZw==/dissolve/50/gravity/SouthEast/dx/10/dy/10"height="168" width="240"/></p><p>White Truffle Tangliolini HK$ 920<br/></p><p>白松露菌和酒中之王Barolo都是意大利Alba的特产，8½建议白松露的食客喝这带有白松露香味的红酒($4180 per bottle) 。</p><p><br/></p><p style="text-align: center"><img src="http://7xj9od.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/1458032380000310.jpg?imageView2/2/w/1000|watermark/1/image/aHR0cDovLzd4ajlvZC5jb20yLnowLmdsYi5xaW5pdWNkbi5jb20vd2F0ZXJtYXJrLnBuZw==/dissolve/50/gravity/SouthEast/dx/10/dy/10"height="319" width="240"/></p><p>Bric Del Fiasc HK$ 4180<br/></p><p>我们只点一杯($420)。不懂饮酒的我们喝不出什么白松露香味，只觉得挺好喝，但又很大一杯。</p><p style="text-align: center"><img src="http://7xj9od.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/145803239100087.jpg?imageView2/2/w/1000|watermark/1/image/aHR0cDovLzd4ajlvZC5jb20yLnowLmdsYi5xaW5pdWNkbi5jb20vd2F0ZXJtYXJrLnBuZw==/dissolve/50/gravity/SouthEast/dx/10/dy/10"height="319" width="240"/></p><p>Bric Del Fiasc By Glass HK$ 420<br/></p><p>来8½不能不吃的还有这Bone-in Rib-Eye (1200g)。索价$1380元，好贵但portion好大，我们6人也吃剩了1/3。这Rib Eye 煎焗至Medium Rare，会先拿出来给我们看，然后再拿回厨房放凉约10分钟，待肉汁回流至肉内，才替客人切件，然后才serve给客人。</p><p><br/></p><p style="text-align: center"><img src="http://7xj9od.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/1458032411000010.jpg?imageView2/2/w/1000|watermark/1/image/aHR0cDovLzd4ajlvZC5jb20yLnowLmdsYi5xaW5pdWNkbi5jb20vd2F0ZXJtYXJrLnBuZw==/dissolve/50/gravity/SouthEast/dx/10/dy/10"height="276" width="240"/></p><p>Bone-In Rib Eye (1200g) HK$ 1380<br/></p><p>等了约15分钟后，我们的Bone-in Rib-Eye已被肢解，分开两碟上。连骨的这碟是较肥的部位。最肥及最熟的部位都是连骨的那边，非常chewy，口感像牛腩，牛味最浓，也是最腻，食一块已足够KO我。右边的那排肉带有肥膏，肉质较软，很香油脂味。</p><p><br/></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align: center"><img src="http://7xj9od.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/145803242400012.jpg?imageView2/2/w/1000|watermark/1/image/aHR0cDovLzd4ajlvZC5jb20yLnowLmdsYi5xaW5pdWNkbi5jb20vd2F0ZXJtYXJrLnBuZw==/dissolve/50/gravity/SouthEast/dx/10/dy/10"height="300" width="240"/></p><p>Bone-in Rib-Eye (1200g) HK$ 1380<br/></p><p>另一碟是较瘦的部位，是perfect的medium rare，没有肥膏，肉质好软身，肉味香甜，女仕们都较爱吃这碟。Rib Eye带有一点点筋，但无须大力嘴嚼也会溶于口内。</p><p><br/></p><p style="text-align: center"><img src="http://7xj9od.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/1458032434000018.jpg?imageView2/2/w/1000|watermark/1/image/aHR0cDovLzd4ajlvZC5jb20yLnowLmdsYi5xaW5pdWNkbi5jb20vd2F0ZXJtYXJrLnBuZw==/dissolve/50/gravity/SouthEast/dx/10/dy/10"height="165" width="240"/></p><p>Bone-in Rib-Eye (1200g) HK$ 1380<br/></p><p><br/></p><p style="text-align: center"><img src="http://7xj9od.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/145803244500054.jpg?imageView2/2/w/1000|watermark/1/image/aHR0cDovLzd4ajlvZC5jb20yLnowLmdsYi5xaW5pdWNkbi5jb20vd2F0ZXJtYXJrLnBuZw==/dissolve/50/gravity/SouthEast/dx/10/dy/10"height="169" width="240"/></p><p>Bone-in Rib-Eye (1200g) HK$ 1380<br/></p><p>Bone-In Rib Eye的配菜同样大堆头，有烤蔬菜及烤薯仔。烤蔬菜有红菜头、cherry tomato、南瓜及甘荀，每种蔬菜都非常清甜和嫩，最推介红菜头，真的超甜。烤薯仔偏爽，薯味好浓。</p><p><br/></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align: center"><img src="http://7xj9od.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/1458032457000713.jpg?imageView2/2/w/1000|watermark/1/image/aHR0cDovLzd4ajlvZC5jb20yLnowLmdsYi5xaW5pdWNkbi5jb20vd2F0ZXJtYXJrLnBuZw==/dissolve/50/gravity/SouthEast/dx/10/dy/10"height="170" width="240"/></p><p>Side dish (assorted Veggie)<br/></p><p><br/></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align: center"><img src="http://7xj9od.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/1458032554000514.jpg?imageView2/2/w/1000|watermark/1/image/aHR0cDovLzd4ajlvZC5jb20yLnowLmdsYi5xaW5pdWNkbi5jb20vd2F0ZXJtYXJrLnBuZw==/dissolve/50/gravity/SouthEast/dx/10/dy/10"height="163" width="240"/></p><p>Side dish (Grill potatoes)<br/></p><p>我们试了多款appetizer，刻意将食评放在精彩的主菜后。foie gras with chestnut soup系Daily Special，鹅肝好滑**，配浓浓的粟子汤汁，是挺特别的配搭。不过我始终prefer鹅肝配偏酸的酱汁。</p><p><br/></p><p style="text-align: center"><img src="http://7xj9od.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/1458032568000218.jpg?imageView2/2/w/1000|watermark/1/image/aHR0cDovLzd4ajlvZC5jb20yLnowLmdsYi5xaW5pdWNkbi5jb20vd2F0ZXJtYXJrLnBuZw==/dissolve/50/gravity/SouthEast/dx/10/dy/10"height="175" width="240"/></p><p>foie gras with chestnut soup HK$ 320<br/></p><p>8½的招牌海鲜汤非常好喝，好浓海鲜味，十分足料。汤料中的白身鱼好滑，两块半生熟的大带子，卖$230元我们都认为超值。</p><p><br/></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align: center"><img src="http://7xj9od.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/1458032579000411.jpg?imageView2/2/w/1000|watermark/1/image/aHR0cDovLzd4ajlvZC5jb20yLnowLmdsYi5xaW5pdWNkbi5jb20vd2F0ZXJtYXJrLnBuZw==/dissolve/50/gravity/SouthEast/dx/10/dy/10"height="168" width="240"/></p><p>Seafood Soup HK$ 230<br/></p><p>鲍鱼薄片配鱼子酱我觉得中规中举，始终鲍鱼是吃其鲜味，这鲍鱼本身鲜味不足，加上鱼子酱的咸，味道并不balanced。</p><p><br/></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align: center"><img src="http://7xj9od.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/1458032589000613.jpg?imageView2/2/w/1000|watermark/1/image/aHR0cDovLzd4ajlvZC5jb20yLnowLmdsYi5xaW5pdWNkbi5jb20vd2F0ZXJtYXJrLnBuZw==/dissolve/50/gravity/SouthEast/dx/10/dy/10"height="167" width="240"/></p><p>Abalone Caviar HK$ 420<br/></p><p>Seared Red Tuna Belly是另一推介头盘，Red Tuna一点也不干，烧得外热内暖，鱼肉非常湿润肥美。鱼味香浓，像Medium Toro多一点。鱼子酱份量多，同刚才的鲍鱼不同，鱼子酱同Tuna蛮搭的。</p><p><br/></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p sty